message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it proposes a fully automatic approach for segmentation of liver and its tumors in CT images using densely connected fully convolutional neural network. It also involves training of neural networks for segmentation which falls under machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with medical imaging (cs.MED) and uses neural networks for segmentation which is a common technique in neuroscience (cs.NEURON).
